Phase 0 — Scaffold & theme
- Next.js 16 App Router + TypeScript + Tailwind v4 setup
- BraunLinear local font (5 weights) via next/font/local
- Full neumorphic design system: CSS custom properties, light/dark tokens,
  .emboss/.deboss/.emboss-interactive utilities, amber glow, ring animations
- Dark mode toggle (useSyncExternalStore, no-flash beforeInteractive script)
- AppFrame with safe-area insets (iPhone notch + home bar)
- BottomNav with swipe gesture support and orange gradient active-tab border
- RootsLogo SVG with orange gradient fill + random-interval diagonal shine
- Screen, AppButton, AppCard, ProgressBar UI shells
- Home, Inventory, Profile placeholder pages

Phase 1 — Contracts
- src/core/types.ts: canonical Section 6 contracts (frozen)
- src/core/copy.ts: passive-speaker reflections, feedback strings, frequency copy
- src/core/data/languages.ts: all 7 languages with exact spec copy
- src/core/data/kinyarwanda/words.ts: 32 words, stable IDs, morpheme breakdowns
- src/core/data/kinyarwanda/lessons.ts: Lessons 0–3 + Pattern Labs 1–2,
  sentence frames, 35 exercises with relatedWordIds for weak-word tracking
- src/core/data/kinyarwanda/patterns.ts: 4 patterns (nd/u/umu/aba), hedged wording
- src/core/data/kinyarwanda/scenarios.ts: grandma-call, 14 dialogue lines
- src/core/data/kinyarwanda/stories.ts: story-grandma-word, 7 panels
- src/core/data/kinyarwanda/texting.ts: elder-safe vs cousin talk
- src/core/data/kinyarwanda/proverbs.ts: 1 demo proverb
- src/core/data/demoUsers.ts: Amara/Daniel demo profiles (Section 11.9)
- src/core/data/index.ts: single data-access boundary (all getters)
- src/core/engine/lessonEngine.ts: buildLessonSteps() with interleaved sequencing
- src/core/engine/answerCheck.ts: checkAnswer(), handles string[] sentence builders
- src/core/engine/patternEngine.ts: renderBreakdown(), swapPrefix(), parseHighlightMarks()
- src/core/engine/reviewEngine.ts: buildReviewSession() with 3 distractors per word
- src/store/useRootsStore.ts: full Zustand persist store, all Section 7 actions
- src/store/useHasHydrated.ts: useSyncExternalStore hydration guard (lint-safe)
- src/lib/supabasePlaceholder.ts: commented placeholder with future table mapping
- src/app/debug/page.tsx: debug page listing lessons + store action buttons

npm run build and npm run lint pass with zero errors.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
